3. Veoma mi je *prijatno* u vašem društvu. (*pleasant*, I feel *pleasant* in your company.)
4. *Prijatni* mirisi cveća šire se parkom. (*pleasant*, *Pleasant* scents of flowers are spreading through the park.)
5. On je vrlo *prijatan* čovek i uvek spreman da pomogne drugima. (*pleasant*, He is a very *pleasant* man and always willing to help others.)
6. Proveo sam *prijatan* vikend sa porodicom na selu. (*pleasant*, I spent a *pleasant* weekend with my family in the countryside.)
7. *Prijatno* veče vam želim! (*pleasantly*, I wish you a *pleasantly* evening!)
8. Ovaj materijal je veoma *prijatan* na dodir. (*pleasant*, This material is very *pleasant* to the touch.)
9. Molim vas da mi *prijatno* iznenadite za moj rođendan. (*pleasantly*, Please *pleasantly* surprise me for my birthday.)
